<html>
  <head>
    <title>getsize</title>
    <link href="./meme-suite.css" rel="styleSheet" type="text/css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="main">
      <script src="./meme-suite-logo.js" type="text/javascript">></script>
      <h1>getsize</h1>
      <p><b>Usage:</b> getsize &lt;datafile&gt; [options]</p>
      <p><b>Description:</b></p>
      <p>
        <code>getsize</code> prints statistics about the sequences in 
        <code><i>&lt;datafile&gt;</i></code>.
      </p>
      <p><b>Input:</b></p>
      <ul>
        <li>A file in <a href="fasta-format.html">FASTA format</a>.
        If the filename is given as "-", then the program reads from
        standard input.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><b>Output:</b></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Writes statistics about the sequences to <code>stdout</code>.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><b>Options:</b></p>
      <ul>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="codons"/></li>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="dna"/></li>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="f"/></li>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="ft"/></li>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="l"/></li>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="nd"/></li>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="prot"/></li>
      <li><command-option program="getsize" name="x"/></li>
      </ul>
      <p><b>Bugs:</b> None known.</p>
      <p><b>Author:</b> Tim Bailey</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
